snippet.title: UNLIT Trailer
snippet.description: In a world where each of the movement you make slowly kills you. Embody a pathfinder went to explore unknown areas of this world. In this adventure you will ahve to plan your route and optimize your movements to reach your objectives before you run out of energy and die.
